hey how is everyone been lately...

its been a while since i have last updated....been working alot as of late...but its actually has been pretty good as of late...dont know y but its been going pretty good...saturday i went to see the prelim show at tate....it was good...saw alot of people....i thought that tates show was very good...sunday i did work all day 10 to 9 ish i think and it was really busy but it went well...i was off again today which was an uneventful day...just pretty much stayed around the house all day...work tomorrow wednesday and then off again on thursday!

everyone have a great week...

daniel!

hey how has everyone been doin???  sorry its been so long since i last updated.  been workin alot lately.  i sprained my ankle at taylors party lol.  its just now starting to feel a little better.  work has been alright lately.  makin money so i cant really complain.  i had a softball game tonight.  we won!  its about time lol thats all ill say about that.  i know i have to work tomorrow night but im not sure about the rest of the week.  everyone have a wonderful week.

daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/11348.html

well its been about a week since the last update so i figured i would let you know how my life is goin.  its been pretty much the same things going on day after day.  work eating and sleeping.   lol.  i sleep an awfully lot.  i like to thank aimee for giving me the night off tonight.  it was gettin to be much needed.  i havent had a softball game in a while.  well we was suppose to have one on tuesday but it got rained out.  i started cooking some at sonnys.  it is a lot tougher than serving or maybe that is just because im new.  im starting to question what i wanna do in life.  oh well hopefully ill figure it out soon.  everyone have a good week.

-dan
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/11054.html

hello everyone...lets sum up my weekend lol...well i worked all of it...and when saturday and sunday i combined to make 300 dollars in tips...sunday was busy all day long...aimee the party you had on saturday night...yeah they diffentely came in at 8:58 but the worst part was...there was 25!! of them...i did not leave until 11:30 which really sucked but on sunday alone i made 170 all day which is the most i ever made in a day.  i gotta work tonight which will be alright.  i actually dont have a day off till next monday..  but ill be ok..  lol  everyone have a great memorial day and watch out if you go to the beach lol many gays around.

-daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/10780.html

how is everyone?  well im off of work till friday.  lol i dont know how i pulled that one off.  i didnt even request for one of the days off.  but ill take it lol.  i have a softball game tonight and thursday night.  i hope we play decently.  umm work has been decent lately.  i still make really good money for sonnys i guess.  summer has been so wonderful so far.  tomorrow night is poker night at marshall's lol.  i should win some money there.  i went to waffle house the past two nights after work.  is there something wrong with that?  being a regular at waffle house lol.  well im off.  ill talk to everyone later.

-daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/10630.html

how is everyone doing tonight...im alright first day off of work in about a week which is really kinda of nice even though im not making any money...but then again life is more than just money.  im also off on thursday and tuesday this week so if you wanna do anything so tell....more than likely ill be bored and wanna do something.  i had a softball game tonight...well it wasnt much of a game...we got killed in four innings lol...thats makes three losses for my team...oh well...there is always next year lol...braves suck...they got no hit by the big unit...oh well everyone have a good night...

-dan
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/10443.html

well well well...im actually updating two days in a row...yall should be proud of me lol.  well today was a unique day i suppose.  lets see where to begin...i woke up this morning around 10...i know what your thinking guys that is way to early for me to get up...but i had to get up and go into work this morning.  i had to be there at 11 and i was on time like usual.  we was busy busy like every other sunday morning.  i made $70 in about 3 hours of work...which is pretty darn good if you ask me.  i actually saw aimee at work for the first time in a long while...lol...she must of got lucky to have all this school because she gets to miss out of all the wonderful world of serving bbq.  i came home from work around 5 and just chillen for most of the night.  the stinkin braves lost again.  oh well.  hopefully they can start winning soon.  ice cream sounds really good right now so i must be going.  talk to everyone later.

-dan "the SB" man
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/10183.html

dont worry everyone dan is still alive and kickin...just been so busy lately from workin that i have had time to update like i would like to.  i wanna start by saying congrats to all the soon to be graduates from high school.  i hope yall are all safe after the graduation and project grad.  i also wanna send out the big heys to meaghan and danielle to really cool girls.  yall are awesome.  i have been workin alot lately but hopefully with school out i will be having more time off now.  fingers are crossed at least.  im still tryin to play some softball at my church, i still suck lol but my team has only lost 2 games so far so thats cool.  i have a game tuesday night and ill be working most of the weekend like usual.  so everyone take it easy.  keep on gellin. 

-dan the man
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/9791.html

hey whats up all ladies and gents? well im doing alright after all im done with school until august some thats extremely cool.  this past weekend hasnt been the best for me though.  i had to spend the majority of it at the real pit serving tables.  even though i did make wonderful money all weekend, i still dont know if it was really worth spending all the time up there, and not gettin to hang out with some of my dearest friends.  but yes life will go on.  this week should be a decent one i think.  i work monday and tuesday night so far.  i dont know the rest of my work schedule yet but i should have friday night off.  and everyone beware mothers day is coming up this weekend. please avoid sonnys if you can...it will be off the chain busy in there. peace out all.

-dan
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/9500.html

well everyone i finally decided to update my journal.  lets see...i guess my life is going alright.  cant really complain about anything.  all i have now left is taking my two exams in school.  work hasnt been that bad lately.  mostly because i havent had to work with mike the wonderful manager lately. lol hear the sarcasism.  i want to send my congrats to the dl for finishing 3rd in san diego.  good job!! well i have a softball game tonight...wish me luck cause i will need it lol.  i have to work pretty much all weekend so come up to sonnys if you wanna see me.

-daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/9338.html

well its seems like lauren and i have decided to just be friends...but im glad that i was able to meet her and all...she is a amazing person...its hard to move on though...

-daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/8997.html

tuesday- i went to class which wasnt all that bad and then i went to work...left work early that night and went to my first softball game of the year...its was fun we won 21-5.

wednesday-all i did was work and i made 80 dollars

thursday-i went to class and then i went to sonnys to find someone to take my shift for the night and then i went to my softball game which we won 17-9 and then i came home and the best part of my day was when a got to talk to this wonderful amazing person for about an hour.

friday-i went up to school and helped set up for the show and me and taylor and matt made signs to put up in the gym...it was interesting watching me trying to paint them...it was worth it though.  i also had a softball game that night. we won a close game 19-16. 

saturday- i woke up and went to school watched many and many guards and drumlines...saw the chaps for maybe the last time this year = ( ...maybe not though...ummm...gave lauren a rose...i think she had a tear in her eye...definitely an unforgetable moment = ) ...

sunday-i worked all day and made close to 150 dollars which was awesome.

monday-just had work made 50 which was bad because i made it out of there rather early.

well...the next few days should be fun...hopefully...

-daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/8788.html

well hello everyone.  i like to start off by saying i had a wonderful weekend.  friday night i worked and closed and made about 80 dollars and then i went over to my friends house and we played some cards till the wee hours in the morning.  saturday was great.  woke up and went to crestview.  i had lots of fun doing that.  sunday i had to wake up early but i went golfing with frank matt and rebecca's brother.  i got a really bad sun burn.  it hurts.  i blew a speaker out in my truck which really sucks.  i also worked last night and made really good money last night.  im off friday and saturday of this week which is exactly what i wanted.  everyone have a great day.  hopefully ill talk to everyone later.

-daniel

ps...i dont wanna go back to school tomorrow!
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/8678.html

wassup journal friends.  how is everyone doing.  im doing pretty good i suppose...i cant really complain that much.  work isnt really that bad anymore well besides the fact that i work most every night.  but i do make decent money where i work.  so it balances out.  brain put in his 3 day notice of quitting to go to a better paying job.  he said servers where he goes walks with making like 200 dollars a night.  im happy for him.  hes a good guy.  i wish i could talk to lauren every single day of the week.  that would be so very awesome.  but its just not happening right now.  hopefully ill see her tomorrow though = ).  she is very very very awesome.  ummm...lets see what else to talk about. im going to crestview on saturday to support some wonderful people at their show this weekend.  sunday morning i am also entered into a golf tourament...kinda scary since i havent went golfing in about a year or so.  hopefully ill do alright.  im in it with matt k.  it should be lots of fun.  everyone please be safe.  i love you all.

-Daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/8208.html

how is everyone.  ill like to start by thanking my good friend matt for picking up my saturday morning shift...i own you one...because he picked it up i was able to see my wonderful friends up at tate during there practice.  saturday night me and taylor were pitchin quarters again whenever a cop drove up behind us.. that was kinda scary lol.  he kept of driving though.  the guard had a wonderful show...especially the person i watched = ) .  then after the show we had to go back up to the school and paint the floor again.  that wasnt that fun but it has to get done.  sunday i opened serving meaning i had to be there at 10 in the morning.. i made 75 dollars in the morning and 35 at night which equals a total of 110 dollars all day which isnt bad at all.  this week is spring break for me so ill be chillen all week.  everyone have a great week.  be safe. 

-dan
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/8112.html

hi.  lets see where i last graced you with the knowledge of my wonderful life.  monday...lets see what all i did.  hmm...woke up had no school...talked to some cool peeps online.  ate a pizza.  it was good.  worked..monday night equals clean bottle night at sonnys which equals hell for daniel.  tuesday i got up and went to both my classes and i also went to pizza hut with my good friend joe nathan reid red man.  i also worked tuesday night..made decent money too.  lets see wednesday i woke up and went and ate lunch with my mommy.  then i chilled at the house till it was time for me to yet again work.  i made 50 bucks and then i got out of there as fast as i could.  i am beginning to hate the smell of that place...well let me restate that...i have never liked the smell of that place.  i have a paper due tomorrow and then i am on spring break...oh yeah.  counting down the hours now...everyone have an outstanding day.

-Daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/7756.html

well hello to all my journal fans...i know that there are so many.. well i left off on thursday.  i had my appointment with chong chew sue chow or whatever his name is, my advisor.  he told to quit my job.  im like...RIGHT ON BUDDY!  thursday i also had to work...i was on a back row again so i didnt make much.  friday i woke up and went to work, just to be on fronts... i am really starting to think that they think that i am a horrible server or something.  oh well...i get out of there early so its all good.  saturday i went up to the cg practice.. right as it ended.. talked to some wonderful people there. and then i went to jonathan's house just to find out that he is going to see a movie with tina as friends on saturday night...oh well i guess he will never learn.  well later on saturday i went to the drumline show and i was able to sit with lauren...yay she is soooo very awesome.  sunday i worked all day long.. didnt make much money...but i worked with really cool people so its all gravy.  everyone have fun during there spring break.. i wont have mine till next week. 

-daniel
http://dan-s-91884.livejournal.com/7492.html

well hello everyone.  where did i leave off from last time.  monday.  i just stayed home all day. i was able to talk to lauren online a little bit = ).  then i went to work that night.  made some money.  i closed on monday with sandy, and we was completely done at 9:00, when a table decided to come in.  so we had to stay there another hour waiting on them.  umm...on tuesday i went to pizza hut to eat lunch with jonathan.  its was fun i suppose.  i worked tuesday night and i was able to leave sonnys at 9, which was cool.  wednesday i went up to the guards practice a little while. i wasnt even able to speak to lauren at all = ( .  oh well.  i worked that night like all other nights.  i was on F and was cut at 7:30 which rocked. i have an appointment in the morning with my advisor.  oh well.  i also work tomorrow night from 3:45 to whenever they decide to cut me.  im happy with my life right now i suppose.  if i could only not work as much. 

-daniel

hello to all.. lets see my weekend.. friday was good.. i woke when to eat at the house that bryan smith built.. and then i went up to tate and started setting up for the regional there.  got to sit with lauren and meaghan during there dinner break some.. lots of fun there = ).. i stayed at tate over night with some the dads because someone had to too make sure everything was groovy.. the regional went well.. the guard had a good finals performance.. got to be with people i like = ) ... umm went to applebees afterwards with lauren, meaghan and joe daddy.  it was great.  hmmm.. got a little sleep saturday night.. worked a double on sunday and made 113 dollars.. screw little, or maybe not so little???, cashiers who are ex-manager's brothers who think they know it all.. the end

Oh yeah Jonathan, I beat you on your freaking American History test... ha ha! i kicked your .... 

Saturday should be fun.  I get to be up at the competition all day long.  And get to go eat afterwards with some good friends = ).
